Converts text to links for contact info.

Example:

	<div id="holder">
		<span class="email">test@test.com</span>
		<span class="phone">555-555-5555</span>
		<span class="twitter">@Twitter</span>
	</div>
	
	$('#holder').informanant({'holder': 'span'});

Arguments:
	holder: HTML tag that data is held in within the container (Default = span)
